    "question_id" : 58125830,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I was facing same problem when I installed JRE by Oracle and solved this problem after my research.</p>\n<p>I moved the environment path\n<code>C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Common Files\\Oracle\\Java\\javapath</code> below <code>H:\\Program Files\\Java\\jdk-13.0.1\\bin</code></p>\n<p>Like this:</p>\n<p>Path</p>\n<p><code>H:\\Program Files\\Java\\jdk-13.0.1\\bin</code><br> <code>C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Common Files\\Oracle\\Java\\javapath</code></p>\n<p>OR</p>\n<p>Path</p>\n<p><code>%JAVA_HOME%</code><br>\n<code>%JRE_HOME%</code></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 2576623,
      "reputation" : 4150,
      "user_id" : 2234161,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 0,
