    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The problem is that you compiled the code with Java 13 (class file 57), and the java runtime is set to Java 8 (class file 52).</p>\n<p>Assuming you have the <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/goldengate/1212/gg-winux/GDRAD/java.htm#BGBFHBEA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">JRE 13 installed</a> in your local system, you could change your runtime from 52 to 57.\nThat you can do with the plugin <strong>Choose Runtime</strong>. To install it go to <em>File/Settings/Plugins</em>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/INhQR.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/INhQR.png\" alt=\"Enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n<p>Once installed go to <em>Help/Find Action</em>, type &quot;runtime&quot; and select the JRE 13 from the dropdown menu.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/NUzB7.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/NUzB7.png\" alt=\"Enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
