    "body" : "<p>How I solved it in Eclipse:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>go to the properties of the project</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/08IGK.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/08IGK.png\" alt=\"Enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>go to Java compiler</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/MIbJ1.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/MIbJ1.png\" alt=\"Enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>change in the Compiler complicated level to the Java version that my project work with (Java 11 in my project).\nYou can see that it your Java that you work when the last message disappear</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Apply</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/RJudk.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/RJudk.png\" alt=\"Enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n"
