      "user_id" : 10225176,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/19b4bb84fa1f9bfd6463c088cf7e7fe5?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "Hani",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/10225176/hani"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 109,
    "last_activity_date" : 1702870259,
    "last_edit_date" : 1702870259,
    "creation_date" : 1633273396,
    "answer_id" : 69426065,
    "question_id" : 58125830,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The easiest solution is to change the Java version in your IDE. In Intellij, go to File --&gt; Project Structure and change the Project SDK to the one that is supported by your Java Runtime (in your case it's 52 which corresponds to version 8 or less). Here's a table that shows the mapping between Java SE Version and Major Version:</p>\n<div class=\"s-table-container\">\n<table class=\"s-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\">Java SE</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\">Major version</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1.0.2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">45</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1.1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">45</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1.2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">46</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1.3</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">47</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1.4</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">48</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">5.0</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">49</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">6</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">50</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">7</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">51</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">8</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">52</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">9</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">53</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">10</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">54</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">11</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">55</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">12</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">56</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">13</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">57</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">14</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">58</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">15</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">59</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">16</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">60</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">17</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">61</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">18</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">62</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">19</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">63</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">20</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">64</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">21</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">65</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p>The table is taken from: <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/specs/jvms/se21/html/jvms-4.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">https://docs.oracle.com/javase/specs/jvms/se21/html/jvms-4.html</a></p>\n"
  }, {
