    "last_activity_date" : 1634965544,
    "creation_date" : 1634965544,
    "answer_id" : 69685297,
    "question_id" : 58125830,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>For eclipse IDE,</p>\n<p>Please follow the below steps -</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Right Click on &quot;Project&quot; -&gt; &quot;properties&quot;</li>\n<li>Click on &quot;Java Compiler&quot;</li>\n<li>Check &quot;Enable Project Specific Setting&quot;</li>\n<li>Correct the &quot;compiler compilation level&quot; ( ref pic is attached )</li>\n<li>If needed, verify and correct java build path for the project as well.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/zMpSR.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/zMpSR.png\" alt=\"Eclipse Project Properties Window\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 7973190,
      "reputation" : 59,
      "user_id" : 6017158,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-q2RC60TzKQs/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAABbU/fTZEDJpyRKI/s256-rj/photo.jpg",
      "display_name" : "veet",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/6017158/veet"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 2,
    "last_activity_date" : 1699142963,
    "last_edit_date" : 1699142963,
    "creation_date" : 1637770467,
    "answer_id" : 70099421,
    "question_id" : 58125830,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>For IntelliJ IDEA 2021.2.3</p>\n<p>After updating Module SDK to openjdk-17, it worked for me.\nopenjdk version &quot;1.8.0_272&quot;</p>\n<p>Menu <em>File</em> → <em>Project Structure</em> → <em>Modules (Project Settings)</em> → <em>Module SDK</em> (select openjdk-17).\nIf openjdk-17 is not there, then from the dropdown, select <em>Add SDK</em> → <em>Download JDK</em> and add openjdk-17.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1207074,
      "reputation" : 4006,
      "user_id" : 1176454,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 84,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/V0rMaYNt.png?s=256",
      "display_name" : "baptx",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1176454/baptx"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 3,
    "last_activity_date" : 1637875960,
    "creation_date" : 1637875960,
    "answer_id" : 70117480,
    "question_id" : 58125830,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>On Linux, I got this error when trying to run SoapUI. Installing the latest OpenJDK JRE package fixed the issue, for example with Ubuntu: <code>sudo apt install openjdk-17-jre</code>.</p>\n<p>I found this question on a search engine, so maybe it will help other people.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 4185179,
      "reputation" : 1334,
      "user_id" : 3429103,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/ac5128cbe5f932467e63e16366161cf3?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "ibra",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/3429103/ibra"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 4,
    "last_activity_date" : 1654169735,
    "creation_date" : 1654169735,
    "answer_id" : 72475609,
    "question_id" : 58125830,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<ol>\n<li>File</li>\n<li>Settings</li>\n<li>Build, Execution, Deployment:</li>\n<li>Compiler</li>\n<li>Java Compiler</li>\n<li>in <strong>Project bytecode version</strong> choose 8</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/KbShe.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/KbShe.png\" alt=\"Intellij Project bytecode version 8\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
